headline: Home Construction Materials Stocks Q1 Highlights: Builders FirstSource (NYSE:BLDR)
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Builders FirstSource (NYSE:BLDR) and the best and worst performers in the home construction materials industry.
